snippet.title: BIRDIE WING Switch Game PV
snippet.description:
Based on the world of BIRDIE WING -Golf Girls' Story-, this game recreates the classic storyline depicted in the anime and lets you play as its main characters. Experience the joys of golf and the thrill of scoring against your opponents!

Learn more: https://htcvive.co/3LbCs9A
